overview: Since a long time ago, Taoon has been thinking of carrying out an operation to seize the jewelry of Emirati artist Ahlam. For this purpose, he is forming a team to assist him in this process. He is recruiting his fiance and her brother with the team. They all go to Sharm el-Sheikh for execution, but they are not alone. They are chased by Officer Safa Shirin Ismat, who was stopped from working in the police force because of Taoon.

production_companies.name: El Sobky Films for Cinema Production

tagline: A comedy about a gang who is trying to rob a famous singer.
title: Ocean 14
